movies.title: Auftauchen
movies.plot: Photography student Nadja Groß (Henriette Heinze) has a lot on her plate, she goes to school, she has a job as a free lancer photographer for a magazine, while economically helping her mother. After a hard day's work she lies to go clubbing. It is in a discotheque she meets Darius (Golo Euler) who is younger than her and an enigmatic character for her. Attraction between the couple suddenly ensues. As they move forward with their very passionate sexual relationship. But strong challenges will be presented in their way. That will test their very foundations.

biography.bio: Henriette Heinze was born in 1973 in Zittau, Saxony, Germany. She is an actress, known for Step on It (2002), Auftauchen (2006) and Paths in the Night (1999).
biography.name: Henriette Heinze

biography.bio: Golo Euler is a German actor. He was born on September 8, 1982 in Starnberg, Germany. From 2002 to 2006 he attended the Bavarian Theater Academy August Everding. The actor is known for the movies Kasimir and Karoline (2011), Westwind (2011), Anderwo (2014) and Grand Budapest Hotel (2014). The last pig (2016) and Fado (2016) are his new upcoming movies.
biography.name: Golo Euler

biography.bio: Sabine Bach was born on September 16, 1956 in Frankfurt am Main, Hesse, Germany. She is an actress, known for The Country Doctor (1987), Berlin Chamissoplatz (1980) and Auftauchen (2006). She was previously married to Nikodemus Frisch.
biography.name: Sabine Bach
